cation of Rex Duo can be used in minimizing yield losses caused by stem rust disease of durum wheat. Therefore, supporting the released durum wheat cultivars with fungicide application is the most pertinent issue in Ethiopia as most of the durum wheat cultivars in farmers hand were moderately susceptible to susceptible cultivars Pgt races.
